  "body": "We are not checking for this rule in gossip block validation:\r\n\r\n```[IGNORE] The block is not from a future slot (with a MAXIMUM_GOSSIP_CLOCK_DISPARITY allowance) -- i.e. validate that signed_beacon_block.message.slot <= current_slot (a client MAY queue future blocks for processing at the appropriate slot).```\r\n\r\nBut we should be.\r\n\r\nPossibly related to #1543 \r\n\r\nDepends on #1547 to replace this function:\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/209924668fc9234c8244b9b8a5f29bf965e39d90/packages/lodestar/src/network/gossip/validation/block.ts#L90\r\nwhich is currently used here:\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/209924668fc9234c8244b9b8a5f29bf965e39d90/packages/lodestar/src/network/gossip/validation/block.ts#L39",
